### 1. Setting a Solid Background Color

You can change the background color using the `background-color` property.

```css
body {
  background-color: #f2f2f2; /* Light gray */
}
```

### 2. Setting an Image Background

To set a background image, use the `background-image` property. The URL of the image is set via the `url()` function. Make sure to adjust the size and position to your liking.

```css
body {
  background-image: url('https://example.com/image.jpg');
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
}
```

